milestones.description: Patterson has broken the record for most ducks (2) in ODIs for SCOT, going past John Blain's 1
Minhajul Abedin and Naimur Rahman's 68-run partnership is BAN's highest for the 6th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 56 between Naimur Rahman and Khaled Mahmud
John Blain and Alec Davies's 20-run partnership is SCOT's highest for the 8th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 12 between John Blain and Alec Davies
Ian Philip has broken the record for most catches (4) in ODIs for SCOT, going past Allingham's 1
Ian Philip has broken the record for most catches in an innings (3) in ODIs for SCOT, going past Allingham's 1
Akram Khan has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (29) for BAN, going past Aminul Islam
Asim Butt has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (3) for SCOT, going past John Blain

stories.title: Scotland's wasted chance
stories.seoTitle: Scotland's wasted chance at the 1999 World Cup
stories.summary: Participation in 1999 was an opportunity to boost the sport's profile in the country - one the cricket board didn't take, leading to a long period in the wilderness
